strings:
<se_def>Brains: Ah, Yangus.
You look pleased with yourself.
Had a spot of luck, have you?

<se_low>Yangus: Too right I 'ave!
I finally found that elucid Moonshadow 'arp!

<se_def>Brains: Well, good for you!
But I thought you were looking for a ship...

<se_low>Yangus: Oh yeah! The ship! Crikey!
I forgot all about it!
Gotta go! Cheers, Brains!

<se_def>Brains: ...Honestly!
Why's he always in such a rush!?
